  "title": "Dozens of golden triangular UFOs observed in Brasília-DF [2001]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/13/dozens-of-golden-triangular-ufos-observed-in-brasilia-df-2001/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-nP",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>FEB 10th, 2001</strong>. Time: 11:17 pm. Duration: 2 minutes. Two people residing in Lago Sul, in Brasília, Distrito Federal, spotted dozens of golden triangular UFOs at an altitude of 12,000ft, making zigzag movements and sometimes going off unexpectedly. According to the witnesses&#8217; account, the UFOs in the firmament appeared to be &#8220;bigger than star&#8221; in size. The UFO was observed with the naked eye under good visibility conditions, and no condensation trails were observed.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.595. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni no Lago Sul em Brasília, Distrito Federal”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n",
